<h1 class="govuk-heading-xl">About this site</h1>

<p class="govuk-body">This site provides a browseable catalogue of AI tools being used in the public sector using public data scraped from the web and provided by the <a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/government-digital-service">Government Digital Service (GDS)</a> in their <a href="https://cddo-af.data.gov.uk/other/public_access/ai_tools_catalogue/AI-tools-catalogue-pilot.html" target="_blank" class="govuk-link">AI Tools Knowledge Graph</a>.</p>

<p class="govuk-body">It was built by <a href="https://www.peterkappus.com/?utm_source=aitools" class="govuk-link">Peter Kappus</a> using <a href="https://www.11ty.dev/" class="govuk-link" target="_blank">11ty</a> and the <a href="https://design-system.service.gov.uk/" class="govuk-link" target="_blank">GOV.UK Design System</a> and a little help from <a href="https://cursor.com/">Cursor</a>.</p>

<h2 class="govuk-heading-m" id="disclaimer">Disclaimer</h2>

<p class="govuk-body">This site was developed independently and is not affiliated with or endorsed by GDS, DSIT, or any other government entity.</p>


<p class="govuk-body">This site is provided AS-IS with no warranty or guarantee of any kind. Data may not be 100% accurate and should always be verified by visiting the source URL for any tool. In no event shall Peter Kappus, PNK Industries Limited, or anyone else be held responsible for any losses suffered as a result of using this service. Use at your own risk. 😀

<p class="govuk-body">Please direct all queries to <a href="https://www.peterkappus.com/contact">Peter Kappus</a>.</p>

<h2 class="govuk-heading-m" id="cookies">Cookies</h2>
<p class="govuk-body">Currently, this site does not use any cookies. I reserve the reigt</p>

<h2 class="govuk-heading-m">Accessibility</h2>
<p class="govuk-body">This service is designed to meet WCAG 2.2 AA.</p>


